---

<section
  id="hero"
  class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-6 overflow-hidden"
>
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900/10 via-slate-900 to-slate-900 pointer-events-none"
  />

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <p class="text-blue-400 font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-6">
      Novi Sad, Serbia
    </p>
    <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight">
      Goran Ljiljak
    </h1>
    <p class="text-slate-300 text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium mb-8">
      Data Engineer &nbsp;·&nbsp; Power BI Developer &nbsp;·&nbsp; SAP Consultant
    </p>
    <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl italic max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      "Data is like coffee — unprocessed, it's just a bean. My job? Brewing it into something
      that keeps your business running!"
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a
        href="#experience"
        class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        View Experience
      </a>
      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="border border-blue-500 text-blue-400 hover:bg-blue-500 hover:text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Contact Me
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
